OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775146264
OL,3,CLife sentence for man who murdered
OL,4,Cbeloved grandmother
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for the life
OL,7,Fafter killing a grandmother to death
OL,8,Fin a violent attack which a family
OL,9,Fsays "turned our lives upside down".
OL,11,FJohn Bootland murdered Colleen
OL,12,FWesterman at a house in the Woodhouse
OL,13,Farea of Leeds in November.
OL,15,FColleen, who was 62, was found at a
OL,16,Fhouse on Melville Gardens with
OL,17,Fmultiple injuries on 6 November after
OL,18,Fpolice were called with reports of a
OL,19,Fdisturbance.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
