CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775146264
OL,3,CLife sentence for man who murdered
OL,4,Cbeloved grandmother
OL,6,FShe was pronounced dead at the scene
OL,7,Fand Bootland was charged two days
OL,8,Flater.
OL,10,FHe was ordered to serve a minimum of
OL,11,F15 years at Leeds Crown Court on
OL,12,FWednesday after pleading guilty to
OL,13,Fmurdering Colleen.
OL,15,FHer family condemned Bootland as
OL,16,F"selfish", saying he had "robbed her
OL,17,Fof her life" and them of their "mum,
OL,18,Fgrandma and daughter".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775146264
OL,3,CLife sentence for man who murdered
OL,4,Cbeloved grandmother
OL,6,FIn a victim impact statement read in
OL,7,Fcourt, one of Colleen's children said:
OL,8,F"My mother was always there for me to
OL,9,Fhelp me when I needed her, especially
OL,10,Fon the times I became anxious as she
OL,11,Fknew how to help my anxiety and calm
OL,12,Fme down.
OL,14,F"She was my rock. You haven't won,
OL,15,Fbecause my mother will live on in my
OL,16,Fheart and many others. My mother's
OL,17,Flegacy will live on forever in the
OL,18,Fpeople who really loved her, whereas
OL,19,Fyou will be forgotten."
OL,26,@{D@WO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775146264
OL,3,CLife sentence for man who murdered
OL,4,Cbeloved grandmother
OL,6,FAnother member of Colleen's family
OL,7,Fsaid: "You were selfish in your
OL,8,Factions, and you had not thought into
OL,9,Fhow it would turn all our lives upside
OL,10,Fdown. I have well and truly lost my
OL,11,Fsmile; I don't know who I am and I
OL,12,Fdon't know if I will find myself
OL,13,Fagain."
OL,15,FDetective Inspector Tom Hilyer, of
OL,16,FWest Yorkshire Police's Homicide and
OL,17,FMajor Enquiry Team (HMET), said: "Our
OL,18,Fthoughts remain firmly with Colleen's
OL,19,Ffamily as they continue to come to
OL,20,Fterms with their loss.
OL,26,@oD@GOUuD@GO]yD@bOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1775146264
OL,3,CLife sentence for man who murdered
OL,4,Cbeloved grandmother
OL,6,F"Bootland's guilty plea prevented them
OL,7,Ffrom having to endure the further
OL,8,Fdistress of a trial, but it doesn't
OL,9,Fbring her back nor excuse what Colleen
OL,10,Fendured on that evening in November.
OL,12,F"I hope today's outcome reflects the
OL,13,Fseriousness of his callous actions,
OL,14,Fand it also provides some measure of
OL,15,Fcomfort to the family that a level of
OL,16,Fjustice has been served, at what
OL,17,Funderstandably continues to be an
OL,18,Fincredibly difficult time for them."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@dO]
